{"tid":2353434,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[2020連登最成功風向選舉]","createTime":"2021-01-04T17:40:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T04:21:14.000Z","uid":22633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f830f4d3bc7bdfbbf3d50c1aa27c3584fcd5cb3e","tid":2353434,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:40:30.000Z","msg":"19年開始嘅逆權運動，<br />\n令連登一時聲名大噪，當日氣勢如虹嘅團結同凝聚力，令猖狂多時嘅五毛PR都無計可施，<br />\n但係經過一段時間嘅專業分析策劃，<br />\n唔使半年佢地已經成功搵返帶風向嘅方法，<br />\n仲越黎越得心應手，<br />\n只需要幾個人，十零個ac，就可以輕鬆一波帶走成班連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要佢地咬邊個就咬邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n向左走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就向左走，<br />\n向右走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就向右走<br />\n<br />\n每一次嘅風向，<br />\n令連登名聲在外，越玩越臭<br />\n每一次嘅批鬥，<br />\n令同路人心灰意冷，越走越遠<br />\n<br />\n今次我地黎總結下2020嘅精彩風向，<br />\n大家一齊黎選出最成功風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.空姐空少落地幸災樂禍<br />\n<br />\n2.木耳被起底報國安<br />\n<br />\n3.攬炒巴被批人血饅頭<br />\n<br />\n4.侵侵輸左，瘋狂屌鳩燒山<br />\n<br />\n以下歡迎大家補充，<br />\n一人一票，一齊黎選出2020 最佳風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c6a038df5b36e05bfd775a13c4a6f7351f9217","tid":2353434,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1d5f7c8dc48e22a95aa068ad2bea437e640fe3d0","tid":2353434,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19c6a038df5b36e05bfd775a13c4a6f7351f9217","tid":2353434,"uid":284432,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:52:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T17:59:34.000Z","msg":"咁N 賓同沙勞咩卡文果啲係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c24c26f